name: CMYK:Split #11 (Static)
description:
On 20/12/2021, Nor44 minted 'CMYK:Split' on FXHash. The automatic capture on the platform didn't grab the thumbnails correctly on 31 of the 256 unique pieces. This is a collection of 1/1s showing what should have been the thumbs for these respective pieces. Nor44 gifted these pieces to the owners of the originals at the time.

------

Description from original piece on FXHash at:
https://www.fxhash.xyz/generative/4111

CMYK:Split uses code to blow apart the CMYK screens used to produce the printed portraits, then scale and position randomly on the X axis.

The four individual female portraits within this piece have been generated using AI.

Please Note: Once your hash-generated composition has been shown the piece will continue to create further infinite compositions.
